Immunization Program Eligibility

The value set to instantiate this attribute should be drawn from a terminologically robust code system that consists of or contains concepts to support describing the patient's elibigility for a vaccination program. This value set is provided as a suggestive example.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/immunization-program-eligibility
